# 🧹 Clean Data

This folder contains the cleaned and processed datasets used for analysis and dashboard development in the **AI Pulse 2030 – Global AI Ecosystem Analysis** project.

## Contents

- Cleaned datasets
- Standardized and formatted data
- Files ready for SQL analysis and Power BI visualization

## Data Cleaning Performed

- Removed duplicate records
- Handled missing values
- Corrected data types
- Standardized text and formats
- Renamed columns for consistency
- Validated data quality

## Notes

- These datasets were created from the **01_Raw** data.
- All analysis, SQL queries, and Power BI dashboards use the files in this folder.
- The cleaned data is optimized for accurate reporting and visualization.
